<span id="freeTextContainer18428676726427982371"><i>The Polar Express </i>is a treasured holiday tradition. This lavish gift set includes a CD audio recording read by Liam Neeson, a keepsake &quot;All Aboard&quot; ornament, and a note from author Chris Van Allsburg.<br/><br/>Awarded the prestigious Caldecott Medal in 1986, <i>The Polar Express </i>has sold more than 7 million copies, become a classic holiday movie, and been translated into stage producti</span>
  <span id="freeText18428676726427982371" style="display:none"><i>The Polar Express </i>is a treasured holiday tradition. This lavish gift set includes a CD audio recording read by Liam Neeson, a keepsake "All Aboard" ornament, and a note from author Chris Van Allsburg.<br /><br />Awarded the prestigious Caldecott Medal in 1986, <i>The Polar Express </i>has sold more than 7 million copies, become a classic holiday movie, and been translated into stage productions that take place across the United States during the holiday season.</span>
